itish political party)/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Peter Bold (died 1762)|Peter Bold]]\n| Tory\n|-\n| 1734\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[James Barry, 4th Earl of Barrymore|The Earl of Barrymore]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| <!-- party -->\n|-\n|March 1747\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Richard Clayton (MP)|Richard Clayton]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| <!-- party -->\n|-\n|June 1747\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Richard Barry (died 1787)|Hon. Richard Barry]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| <!-- party -->\n|-\n| 1754\n| style=\"background-color: {{Tories (British political party)/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Sir William Meredith, 3rd Baronet|Sir William Meredith]]\n| [[Tories (British political party)|Tory]]\n|-\n| 1761\n| style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Fletcher Norton, 1st Baron Grantley|Fletcher Norton]]\n| <!-- party -->\n| style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Simon Luttrell, 1st Earl of Carhampton|Simon Luttrell]]\n| <!-- party -->\n|-\n| 1768\n|rowspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[George Byng (1735\u20131789)|George Byng]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"| <!-- party -->\n| style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Beaumont Hotham, 2nd Baron Hotham|Beaumont Hotham]]\n| <!-- party -->\n|-\n| 1775\n| style=\"background-color: {{Tories (British political party)/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[John Morton (MP)|John Morton]]\n| [[Tories (British political party)|Tory]]\n|-\n|August 1780\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Henry Simpson Bridgeman]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| <!-- party -->\n|-\n|September 1780\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{Tories (British political party)/meta/color}}\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Horatio Walpole, 2nd Earl of Orford|Hon. Horatio Walpole]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Tories (British political party)|Tory]]<ref name=\"stooks-smith\">{{cite book\n |last=Stooks 